review: I am very happy with the service provided by Dr. Aysha Mansoor. She is very gentle while doing the treatment, has got lots of patience, explains very step before doing it and the most important thing she cares for the patients comfort level. She keeps asking the patient if they are fine if they are facing any discomfort. If we indicate any discomfort then she tries to modify her actions so that the patient feels more comfortable. She is too good with kids. My daughter loves going to her and cooperates very well with the doctor.  Even if it's kids she explains them everything before doing anything and also takes their permission before starting the procedure. Overall great experience with the doctor and would definitely recommend her to my known circle.

review: Taken treatment from Dr.Aysha mansoor for root canal for my 6 years old daughter. She explained the possible reasons for the problems which is very unique and didn't hear this reason from other doctor. The details about the treatment with rates explained well before. We went for 3 sittings and overall we had a smooth execution.  Doctor has explained about precaution to be taken care after the treatment. The laughing gas treatment is fine for kids. Doctor is kind and treat kids with care and all the staff are good. They did follow up about the kids condition after the treatment. I would surely recommend for any dental issue.
